    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うわぁ……！
空気が美味しい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wow! The air here is so fresh!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278748</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>他のところに比べると
マナの濃度が高いんだよ、
きっと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Compared to other places, the density
of mana is much higher here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279080</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしました？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is something the matter?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私の育った森に
すごく似てる気がするんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This really resembles the forest
I grew up in. It brings back a
lot of old memories...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この神聖な空気が、
精霊の森って感じ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The feeling of holiness within
this forest...it's the same as
the Forest of Spirits.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊の森……？
君は精霊の森で育ったのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Forest of Spirits...? You mean you've
been living in the Forest of Spirits?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>別に隠してたわけじゃ
ないんだけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh yeah. I wasn't trying to
hide it or anything, though.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279740</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうか……あの森で……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh yeah... It was in that forest...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あのさ……
そろそろ行かね？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, are we going or what?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_220_050_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだな。
行こう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's right. Let's move.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
